question: Transfer counts by care unit
expected_sql: SELECT * FROM ( SELECT CAREUNIT, COUNT(*) AS cnt FROM TRANSFERS WHERE CAREUNIT IS NOT NULL GROUP BY CAREUNIT ORDER BY cnt DESC ) WHERE ROWNUM <= 10
generated_sql: SELECT TRANSFERS.CAREUNIT, COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM TRANSFERS WHERE TRANSFERS.CAREUNIT IS NOT NULL GROUP BY TRANSFERS.CAREUNIT ORDER BY CNT DESC

question: 진단 코드가 어떤 체계(버전)로 기록됐는지(예: ICD-9/ICD-10) 비중을 알려줘.
expected_sql: SELECT d.icd_version, COUNT(*) AS dx_row_cnt FROM DIAGNOSES_ICD d JOIN ADMISSIONS a ON a.hadm_id = d.hadm_id GROUP BY d.icd_version ORDER BY dx_row_cnt DESC FETCH FIRST 10 ROWS ONLY
generated_sql: SELECT ICD_VERSION, COUNT(DISTINCT HADM_ID) / (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT HADM_ID) FROM DIAGNOSES_ICD) AS proportion FROM DIAGNOSES_ICD GROUP BY ICD_VERSION
